<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation - Staples Store</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <button class="menu-button" onclick="toggleMenu()">Menu</button>
        <h1>Order Confirmation</h1>
    </header>

    <main>
        <h2>Thank you for your order, <%= name %>!</h2>

        <p>Your order has been approved and will be shipped in <%= deliveryTime %>.</p>

        <div class="order-details">
            <h3>Order Details</h3>
            <div class="product">
                <img src="/images/<%= product.image %>" alt="<%= product.name %>" style="width: 100px;">
                <div class="product-info">
                    <h4>
                        <%= product.name %> (<%= color %>)
                    </h4>
                    <p>
                        <%= product.price %> CAD
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3>Shipping Information</h3>
            <p><strong>Name:</strong>
                <%= name %>
            </p>
            <p><strong>Address:</strong>
                <%= address %>, <%= city %>, <%= postalCode %>, <%= country %>
            </p>
            <p>Your order will be shipped to this address and delivered within the next <%= deliveryTime %>.</p>
        </div>

        <h3>Shipping Details</h3>
        <p>We aim to deliver your products within the specified delivery time. If there are any delays, you will be
            notified via email. In the meantime, you can always track your order on our website.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team at
            <strong>support@staplesstore.com</strong>.</p>

        <h3>Delivery Instructions</h3>
        <p>Once your order is shipped, you will receive a tracking number via email. Please allow 1-2 business days for
            processing before your order ships. We use trusted delivery partners to ensure your product arrives safely
            and on time.</p>
    </main>

    <div class="menu" id="menu">
        <ul class="menu-list">
            <li><a href="#">Laptops</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Phones</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Accessories</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Tablets</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Offers</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Gaming</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Smart Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">TV & Audio</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Wearables</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Clearance</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <script>
        function toggleMenu() {
            var menu = document.getElementById('menu');
            menu.classList.toggle('show');
        }
    </script>

</body>

</html>